channel.title: Help on compiling
channel.description: Hey, Just made new pk server. Lots of players, working fine. But now when I update and compile, it says its fine. But then Nothing changes. I also can't see any items except a few and I cant see barrages and things, All the other players can see fine.

“C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.6.0_03\bin\javac.exe” *.java
pause
